{"tid":1482232,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警無權進入私人地方！請廣傳","createTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:07:19.000Z","uid":285481,"like":65,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"974ac94db464711e7f4f5246feb5da6c56f929e8","tid":1482232,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:05.000Z","msg":"請廣傳比身邊朋友，支援良心物業管理員！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kiw5nrY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkiw5nrY.jpg&h=4dc068f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c53941918c9793ecd20a7f1c5c41bd0bbeed1d","tid":1482232,"uid":285481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:28.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"aa9184b3aea904571b6869af2ef26735f2582a1d","tid":1482232,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:38.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"d8a4a5ef097816d7464a5883990c5bf6149ea0c2","tid":1482232,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:33:48.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"8842ac777c7e69c2749734deb54d21879c0235e7","tid":1482232,"uid":139409,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:34:17.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【英重量級議員 促給港人完整英國國籍】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnf9O7G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbnf9O7G.jpg&h=5ee9af01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n// 英國下議院外交委員會主席圖根達特（Tom Tugendhat）呼籲，政府應給予香港人完整的英國國籍，作為與北京對峙的一種保障。（法新社）//<br />\n<br />\n👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻👇🏻<br />\n<br />\n1分鐘時間幫幫手簽<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 就打0852<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=cbd28f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a><br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\nQ: 簽咗咁多聯署 / 英國佬唔會幫我地 / 英國佬講咗咁耐都冇做過嘢簽嚟都冇用<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗1分鐘搞掂又冇成本嘅嘢點解唔做咗先 <br />\n<br />\n六合彩咁難中你又買<br />\n夠10萬個就有機會喺英國國會討論<br />\n<br />\n今次係有下議會議員帶頭講要俾full citizenship BNO holder<br />\n10萬人都簽唔到叫人地點幫你啊<br />\n我地要送子彈啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n🔥⭐️Q: 好多97後都冇BNO 我地唔可以扔低佢地⭐️🔥<br />\n<br />\nA: 有BC又有幾多人會即刻走 <br />\n反而有咗後路可以更盡情咁去抗爭<br />\n同埋到時大量英國國民喺香港 可以增加英國嘅談判籌碼<br />\n真係去到最壞情況都可以諗方法帶埋d細路走<br />\n<br />\nQ: 佢要tick Only British citizens or UK residents have the right to sign<br />\n我 得 / 冇BNO簽唔簽得？<br />\n<br />\nA: 唔洗verify citizenship 自己諗簽唔簽<br />\n只要提供 email address + 英文名 ＋選Location + Postal code<br />\n<br />\nQ: Postal code 打咩好？<br />\n<br />\nA: 記住喺香港住嘅tick返Hong Kong<br />\nPostal code 成功例子參考<br />\n852 <br />\n0852 <br />\n00000 <br />\n000000<br />\n<br />\n再貼多次條Link:<br />\n<br />\nBritish National (Overseas) Citizens should be given full British Citizenship.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.parliament.uk%2Fpetitions%2F244402&d=MqHS405OUPR0rJ167hdmPIuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=cbd28f0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://petition.parliament.uk/petitions/244402</a>"},{"pid":"0ed67eccaa1064fd0c35a5557ab17b23904ba8c5","tid":1482232,"uid":269221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:36:37.000Z","msg":"818 陣間見"},{"pid":"18008eca72781822dea8024e9c12f7f75001f11d","tid":1482232,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T04:37:20.000Z","msg